- content_for :title do
    Reset password
%p
    You are resetting password for
    %strong
        #{@user.full_name} (#{@user.login})
    \. However, a password reset is pending and still valid. If you reset password
    now, the previous instructions for password reset will be invalidated.
%p
    Are you sure you want to reset the account's password?
= form_tag admin_user_reset_password_path(@user), method: :post, class: 'right' do
    = link_to 'Cancel', admin_user_path(@user), class: 'button secondary'
    = hidden_field_tag 'confirm', '1'
    = submit_tag 'Reset password', class: 'button'
